{"tid":1840727,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣勸台商染肺炎大陸治 武漢醫療水平很不錯","createTime":"2020-01-25T03:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:56:04.000Z","uid":144372,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d0a69ae79e8e3b43192af94c867247963e5d851","tid":1840727,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0123/805413.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2020%2F0123%2F805413.shtml&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT7sYlYTGbxuQQGsxDmAgPG8%3D&h=dfeafb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0123/805413.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n據台灣媒體報道，一台商抱病從大陸搭機回台，結果確診為此次新型冠狀病毒感染的肺炎，引發島內討論。島內流行疫情指揮中心發言人莊人祥今天說，一般建議在當地生病應在當地就醫，或可登機前由航空公司評估是否適航。<br />\n<br />\n  台灣出現1例新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎病例。該病患是一名55歲的台商。她在武漢發病9天後搭機回台，在機上全程戴口罩，僅吃飯時拿下口罩，且主動跟檢疫人員告知身體不適，隨即被送隔離。<br />\n<br />\n  台大醫院小兒部主任黃立民上午在記者會上建議，台商如果在大陸感到身體不適，最好在大陸治療、不要移動，武漢的醫療水平也不錯，且大陸也累積了不少經驗。"},{"pid":"ccf8facbe45ba12c37437ff8a91437a828371817","tid":1840727,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4a56833b118d8ae44471e81e76129e58f2d2335","tid":1840727,"uid":272652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:43:49.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e28c2a37e99777bc3ac7bd5cbc0b8c13348b968","tid":1840727,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T03:50:28.000Z","msg":"台灣No.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aeaaa76b3a01c54f1d5fd8a23aa51433a14c4f","tid":1840727,"uid":299537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"大陸也累積了不少經驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}